      <h3>{{_i}}Disabled state{{/i}}</h3>
      <p>{{_i}}For disabled buttons, use <code>.btn-disabled</code> for links and <code>:disabled</code> for <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> elements.{{/i}}</p>
